def module Y
def desc Press "Y" for safe anchor

on key_press Y if targeting_block !if target_block #air switch #anchor then input right then wait 0.05 then switch :glowstone then input right then wait 0.05 then hold_input sneak 0.05 then wait 0.05 then input right then wait 0.05 then switch #totem